How to build primesieve (Windows, Linux, Mac OS X)
==================================================

  1. Download and install the Qt SDK from:
     http://qt.nokia.com/downloads

  2. Launch the primesieve.pro file with the Qt-Creator IDE and have
     a look at Qt-Creator-build-settings.png for the build settings.

Remarks
=======

  primesieve has been developed with Qt 4.7, if it does not compile
  with future releases of Qt old Qt4 builds can be retrieved from:
  ftp://ftp.trolltech.com/qt/source/

  The compiled primesieve executable depends on the QtGui4 and QtCore4
  libraries (Windows: .dll, Unix: .lib). You need to copy these
  libraries into the primesieve executable directory if you want to
  run it on other PCs.
